trans-unit.source: Represents an association set in the conceptual model.
trans-unit.target: Representa um conjunto de associações no modelo conceitual.

trans-unit.source: In CSDL, an <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet> contains the instances of the <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType>.
trans-unit.target: No CSDL, um <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet> contém as instâncias de <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType>.
Para obter mais informações, consulte [conjuntos de associação (EDM)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/a1d39938-e52c-4293-b676-87ee6afe52e5).

trans-unit.source: A collection of type <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" /> that contains the ends of this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de tipo <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" /> que contém as extremidades deste <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the built-in type kind for this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a variante do tipo interno para este <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind" /> object that represents built-in type kind for this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind" /> objeto que representa o tipo interno para este <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the association related to this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a associação relacionada a este <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType" /> object that represents the association related to this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType" /> objeto que representa a associação relacionados a este <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet" />.
